 -->
    <p class=" mx-auto max-w-[1200px]  lg:max-h-[104px] font-merriweather text-[20px] md:text-[32px] font-normal leading-[2.375rem] md:leading-[3.25rem] justify-center  md:text-center text-justify text-[#49494C]">{subTitle}</p>
    
  </div>